						<div class="postbody">tokumaru, when you say "metatile index" what does that mean?  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" />  Is it a number that I'm susposed to give each metatile?  This is not worked out well enough in my head...  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" />  yet.   Yes, I would like to set the upper two bits of this metatile index to the pallet and  decrease the number of bytes used for each metatile!  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />
